      "content": "the silence sounds nice though. a lot more peaceful than always trying to find meaning or \"find myself\" or whatever. i feel like i've been doing so much work just to get to this point, and i'm just... exhausted. there's a certain kind of peace in knowing that every journey has a final destination, and maybe it's okay to just reach it. to finally be done with the road.",
